    "## DESCRIPTION:\n",
    "Implement a function which convert the given boolean value into its string representation.\n",
    "\n",
    "Note: Only valid inputs will be given.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Solution:\n",
    "```python\n",
    "def boolean_to_string(b):\n",
    "    return 'True' if b else 'False'\n",
    "```"
